Class DivFast

java.lang.Object
  Code.DSA.DivFast

public class DivFast
extends java.lang.Object

This class implements a faster method of division. for a 32 bit number the maximum number of comparision (worst case scenario) is 31+31 = 62 times. and maximum number of subtraction and additions are 31 each.
